text: Chelsea Brown (December 6, 1942 – March 27, 2017) was an American-Australian actress and comedian. She appeared as a regular performer in comedy series Rowan & Martin's Laugh-In. She was also known for her roles in the soap operas Number 96 (in 1977), and E Street (in 1990–1991). Brown was born in Chicago, Illinois. She was married to Vic Rooney until her death in 2017.
